{"tid":1673353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"養心殿荃灣店未開業已連裝修拍賣","createTime":"2019-10-24T15:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T15:05:14.000Z","uid":185631,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"85ac413beb26bf9e1b3ba39620db839dd60570d9","tid":1673353,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:15:43.000Z","msg":"【Kelly Online】養心殿荃灣店未開業已連裝修拍賣<br />\n<br />\n反修例風波持續四個多月，飲食零售業首當其衝。不少食肆更被不同立場的網民聲討，其中台式火鍋連鎖店「養心殿」，因老闆曾指「示威者是收錢才上街」等言論，被網民列入「罷食」名單。「養心殿」近月多間分店陸續在門外貼張貼告示，指因租約期滿而結業。昨日再有網民發現，「養心殿」位於荃灣廣場地庫的分店，原定今年9月開業，卻突然在門外圍上圍板，貼出告示，指將會拍賣該店店內的裝修物品。養心殿老闆回應傳媒查詢就指「社會亂」，難再開新店。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣廣場地庫「養心殿」分店原定今年9月開業，卻在門外圍上圍板並貼出告示，指將會拍賣該店店內的裝修物品。 網民Sharon Ho圖"},{"pid":"d4c617f8dcaa1d197c0abf94054dc4f40c48ded7","tid":1673353,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCA3VqG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCA3VqG.jpg&h=1b492863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNvkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=415e16ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c40a83fa315bb57c7dd624fb393bee7aafdea2af","tid":1673353,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:26:50.000Z","msg":"我就係要呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cdea7ca9fd5eee4ac52b4771ed332bab74448d","tid":1673353,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8c3ae356061476927476a9ee5534b88d84f0b4be","tid":1673353,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:05:14.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}